At  2/18/2008 01:50 PM, George Lyle wrote:

>The puller is a great idea,  I don't see a way to reinstall the CV with the
>puller, though.  Back to the brass hammer...

Putting it back together was even easier.
Got it started and resting in the grooves, put a wood chunk on top 
(covered the whole joint) and smacked it with the hammer. To push it 
more than flush I used a deep socket and tapped it down.



